884
00:47:57,458 --> 00:47:58,708
Pogramy w golfa.

885
00:47:58,791 --> 00:48:01,500
Szkoda, bo gram jeszcze
gorzej niż w tenisa.

886
00:48:01,583 --> 00:48:02,708
„Pogramy”?

887
00:48:05,291 --> 00:48:06,708
Ja i Sophia.

888
00:48:10,541 --> 00:48:12,083
Często się widujecie.

889
00:48:12,166 --> 00:48:13,666
